Features: 12 different adult images to reveal at high resolution Cards are shuffled randomly at each game, for maximum replay value. Timer, to see how long it takes to solve a puzzle Gallery where you can view all the puzzle images you have solved. Relaxing music. Be among the fastest players to achieve a top spot in our Leaderboards and unlock various achievements.
